 <p>
  <b>Rule-14 ᐅ </b>
  Gerund combinations যেমন: suggest/recommend/advise/propose+ gerund+ object-যুক্ত active voice-এর passive কাঠামো ᐅ
 </p>
 <card>Active voice-এর subject+ মূল verb+ that+ gerund-এর পরের object+ should be+ gerund-কে verb-এ পরিণত করে তার past participle.</card>
 <h3>Example ᐅ </h3>
 <ul>
  <li>He proposed watching the movie. (Active)</li>
  <li>He proposed that the movie should be watched. (Passive)</li>
 </ul>
